10/20/30 Rule of Presentation ^section

Ten slides, no more than twenty minutes, no font smaller than thirty points, G. Kawasaki

The ten topics that a venture capitalist cares about are:

- Problem
- Your solution
- Business model
- Underlying magic/technology
- Marketing and sales
- Competition
- Team
- Projections and milestones
- Status and timeline
- Summary and call to action

